 * Themed inline: the plate/lens paint with `currentColor` (= the page --accent, so corail on the
 * home header and violet elsewhere) and the knockout paints with --color-paper. Rendered inline
 * (not <img>) precisely so currentColor resolves against the surrounding link colour.
 */
